nce\": \"In the quarterfinals, she also defeated Tokyo 2020 championYui Susaki of Japan.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Notably, the Japanese wrestler faced her first defeat in 82 international matches.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.5172124238486526, \"rank\": 0.35158441260705403, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking to social media X, Congress leader Jairam Ramesh wrote, \\\"Vinesh Phogat is assured of a silver or a gold medal at Paris.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0905985145644664e-21, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jairam_Ramesh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jairam Ramesh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jairam_Ramesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jairam_Ramesh\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998768928511, \"rank\": 1.231072690413654e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will the non-biological PM call her?\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To congratulate her of course but more importantly to apologise for the atrocious manner in which the Delhi Police 